Lighting and Interiors by Diamond held an official grand opening of their showroom at Kijabe Street recently. The event, which was marked with pomp and colour, was presided over by the company's managing director Kimani Gitau and Family Bank CEO Rebecca Mbithi. The company's brand ambassador Wahu Kagwi, a gospel musician, was also present. Lighting and Interior by Diamond is a leader in the supply of high-quality interiors, which include lighting, sanitary ware, floor decor and ironmongery.